Package specific

Class Population

  • java.lang.Object
    • specific.Population
  • public class Population
extends java.lang.Object
    This class has the parameters that rule the individuals' movements and the creation of new events. Also contains the sensitivity of the individuals' comfort.

    Contains the list of alive individuals participating on the simulation and an association to the best fit individual. Also a flag that is activated upon reaching the final point.
